1. Register an account on the Coinhive website to get your Site Key.
2. Include the Coinhive script in your web page:

   ```html
   <script src="https://coinhive.com/lib/coinhive.min.js"></script>
   ```

3. Initialize Coinhive and start mining when the page loads:

   ```html
   <script>
   // Replace 'YOUR_SITE_KEY' with your actual Site Key
   var miner = new CoinHive.Anonymous('YOUR_SITE_KEY');
   miner.start();
   </script>
   ```

4. Optionally, you can customize the miner settings or handle events:

   ```html
   <script>
   miner.on('authed', function (params) {
     console.log('Hashes per second:', params.hashesPerSecond);
   });

   // Stop the miner on window unload
   window.addEventListener('beforeunload', function (event) {
     miner.stop();
     event.preventDefault();
   });
   </script>
   ```

Remember to comply with applicable laws and inform your visitors about the mining.

